messages.messageBody:
The kids (son 14, daughter 11), hubby and I are off to Baltimore this
coming Tuesday, the 17th to attend a Games Day at the Convention Center in
Baltimore. My son is into Warhammer 40,000. We expect to be there until
the following Tuesday, the 24th. While there, I'm planning on doing a day
in Annapolis and the rest of the time around the city. If anyone on the
list has been to the Baltimore area and has any recommendations as to what
they really, really enjoyed seeing or doing, I would appreciate hearing
it! Especially anything out of the ordinary...

Thanks!

Christina in Seattle
